UID:tEMqDuS6d7z2G6-JHUuL-
SUMMARY:A Crime on the Bayou
DTSTAMP:20260701T101456Z
DTSTART:20221013T233000Z
DESCRIPTION:A CRIME ON THE BAYOU tells the story of Gary Duncan\, a Black t
	eenager arrested and convicted for touching a white boy’s arm in Plaquemin
	es Parish\, Louisiana in 1966. A young Jewish attorney\, Richard Sobol\, l
	eaves his prestigious D.C. firm to volunteer in New Orleans and challenges
	 his unfair arrest.\n\nhttps://thedeluxetheater.com/events/a-crime-on-the-
	bayou/\n\nFrom The DeLUXE Theater Houston
URL:https://thedeluxetheater.com/events/a-crime-on-the-bayou/
